  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc7 9 \u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd; \u0b9a\u0bc1.\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "May 9 incidents of violence; S. Gavi's important person arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Following the violent incidents that took place in the country on May 09, a member of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party has been arrested in connection with the violent incidents in Piliyandal.",
        "A Freedom Party member of Kesbewa Municipality has been arrested. Investigations have revealed that the suspect is connected with 6 incidents of violence in Piliyandala.",
        "According to the police, the suspect is connected to 6 violent incidents including the attack and damage to the house of Kesbewa Mayor Laxman Perera, the attack on his sister's house and the attack on the house of Kamini Lokke MP's brother."
      ],
